I thank you! You must have a rest. Be at the levee to- morrow after the parade. However, I will let you know." 
The stupid smile, which had left his face while he was speaking, reappeared. 
"Au revoir! Thank you very much. His Maj- esty will probably desire to see you," he added, bowing his head.
